# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:11
translate french jamiephone1_8f448c11:

    # "I feel my phone buzzing and pull it out of my pocket."
    "Je sens mon téléphone vibrer et je le sors de ma poche."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:13
translate french jamiephone1_9d0e5e2b:

    # "It's Jamie. I answer and lie down on the bed to talk."
    "C'est Jamie. Je réponds et je m'allonge sur le lit pour parler."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:18
translate french jamiephone1_14dc4818:

    # pc "Hey"
    pc "Salut"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:20
translate french jamiephone1_e6b33c25:

    # gnd "Hey, [pcname]. How's it going?"
    gnd "Salut, [pcname]. Comment ça va ?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:21
translate french jamiephone1_d57f9715:

    # pc "Pretty good, what's up?"
    pc "Plutôt bien, quoi de neuf ?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:22
translate french jamiephone1_ab588a54:

    # gnd "Just felt like talking to you. You got some time?"
    gnd "J'avais juste envie de te parler. Tu as un peu de temps ?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:25
translate french jamiephone1_cf8b9e59:

    # pc "Sure, I got time."
    pc "Bien sûr, j'ai le temps."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:29
translate french jamiephone1_c2cf9bb6:

    # gnd "Wow, natural charmer aren't ya?"
    gnd "Waouh, t'es un charmeur né, hein ?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:30
translate french jamiephone1_80cdcc09:

    # pc "I like talking to you."
    pc "J'aime bien te parler."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:31
translate french jamiephone1_5d93fddb:

    # gnd "Good. I like talking to you too."
    gnd "Tant mieux. Moi aussi, j'aime bien te parler."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:34
translate french jamiephone1_ca582ae4:

    # gnd "Oh, that's too bad. I'll talk to you some other time then."
    gnd "Oh, c'est dommage. On se reparlera une autre fois alors."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:35
translate french jamiephone1_66ec96d3:

    # gnd "Sorry to bother you. Talk to you later."
    gnd "Désolé de t'avoir dérangée. À plus tard."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:36
translate french jamiephone1_f01523d0:

    # "She hangs up the phone and I put it back into my pocket."
    "Elle raccroche et je remets le téléphone dans ma poche."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:42
translate french jamiephone1_62e5dd7e:

    # pc "So what's going on?"
    pc "Alors, qu'est-ce qui se passe ?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:44
translate french jamiephone1_d8868bcd:

    # gnd "Just been a rough week at school."
    gnd "J'ai juste eu une semaine difficile à l'école."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:45
translate french jamiephone1_d87c0f62:

    # pc "Really? You're usually so good at school. What are you struggling with?"
    pc "Vraiment ? D'habitude, tu es si bon à l'école. Qu'est-ce qui te pose problème ?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:46
translate french jamiephone1_7e66235e:

    # gnd "I'm not really struggling with any of the schoolwork."
    gnd "Ce n'est pas vraiment le travail scolaire qui me pose problème."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:47
translate french jamiephone1_43b9e385:

    # gnd "It's the in-class teaching program."
    gnd "C'est le programme d'enseignement en classe."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:48
translate french jamiephone1_d6457b46:

    # gnd "I have to stand in front of all of these students and teach."
    gnd "Je dois me tenir devant tous ces élèves et enseigner."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:49
translate french jamiephone1_bc8e7906:

    # gnd "I'm just having a hard time standing at the front of the class with all of them looking at me."
    gnd "J'ai juste du mal à me tenir devant la classe alors qu'ils me regardent tous."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:50
translate french jamiephone1_c80b503a:

    # pc "You're scared of public speaking?"
    pc "Tu as peur de parler en public ?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:51
translate french jamiephone1_15bcf641:

    # gnd "I guess so. I've never really had to do a lot of it. It's just uncomfortable having all eyes on me. It makes me really self-conscious."
    gnd "Je suppose. Je n'ai jamais vraiment eu à le faire souvent. C'est juste gênant d'avoir tous les regards braqués sur moi. Ça me rend vraiment mal à l'aise."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:54
translate french jamiephone1_1eff5d82:

    # gnd "I'm sure you're right, it's just hard right now."
    gnd "Je suis sûr que tu as raison, c'est juste difficile en ce moment."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:57
translate french jamiephone1_b138a837:

    # gnd "What do you mean?"
    gnd "Comment ça ?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:58
translate french jamiephone1_ecd76308:

    # pc "Well you're beautiful. I'm sure that guys stare at you all the time."
    pc "Eh bien, tu es belle. Je suis sûr que les garçons te regardent tout le temps."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:59
translate french jamiephone1_c31f5d75:

    # gnd "You think I'm beautiful?"
    gnd "Tu me trouves belle ?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:60
translate french jamiephone1_dd9bd446:

    # pc "Of course you are."
    pc "Bien sûr que oui."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:62
translate french jamiephone1_a5543b0a:

    # gnd "Thanks, [pcname]."
    gnd "Merci, [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:63
translate french jamiephone1_92d2aff8:

    # gnd "But as nice as that is, it doesn't really help me with the public speaking."
    gnd "Mais même si c'est gentil, ça ne m'aide pas vraiment à parler en public."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:66
translate french jamiephone1_9cc47622:

    # gnd "[pcname]!"
    gnd "[pcname] !"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:67
translate french jamiephone1_58f48bda:

    # gnd "I've heard of that method before, but in this case the audience is a bunch of thirteen-year-olds."
    gnd "J'ai déjà entendu parler de cette méthode, mais dans ce cas-là, le public est composé d'une bande d'adolescents de treize ans."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:68
translate french jamiephone1_84faa7b7:

    # pc "Oh right. Not a good idea then."
    pc "Ah oui, c'est vrai. Ce n'est pas une bonne idée alors."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:70
translate french jamiephone1_ba2f8001:

    # gnd "Right. Bad idea, try again."
    gnd "Exactement. Mauvaise idée, on recommence."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:71
translate french jamiephone1_c0af307c:

    # pc "Maybe you could practice your lessons ahead of time on me?"
    pc "Tu pourrais peut-être répéter tes cours à l'avance avec moi ?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:73
translate french jamiephone1_032af84e:

    # gnd "You'd do that for me?"
    gnd "Tu ferais ça pour moi ?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:74
translate french jamiephone1_2bf7afc7:

    # pc "Sure, just let me know and I'll listen to your lessons. Then during class, you can just pretend that you're giving your lessons to me again."
    pc "Bien sûr, dis-le-moi et j'écouterai tes cours. Ensuite, en classe, tu n'auras qu'à faire comme si tu me donnais à nouveau tes cours."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:75
translate french jamiephone1_73d793ae:

    # pc "After a while, the butterflies will probably go away."
    pc "Au bout d'un moment, le trac disparaîtra probablement."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:77
translate french jamiephone1_cadb83e9:

    # gnd "That's actually a pretty good idea."
    gnd "C'est en fait une très bonne idée."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:78
translate french jamiephone1_79c9211e:

    # pc "I have them occasionally."
    pc "Ça m'arrive de temps en temps."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:80
translate french jamiephone1_8dab1990:

    # gnd "Thanks, [pcname]. I'll let you know when I need you to listen to a lesson."
    gnd "Merci, [pcname]. Je te dirai quand j'aurai besoin que tu écoutes un cours."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:81
translate french jamiephone1_050f909c:

    # pc "Sounds good."
    pc "Ça me va."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:82
translate french jamiephone1_1bf27b6a:

    # gnd "Have you been doing okay in school?"
    gnd "Ça se passe bien à l'école ?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:83
translate french jamiephone1_f033e017:

    # pc "It's been going okay so far."
    pc "Ça se passe bien pour l'instant."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:85
translate french jamiephone1_5e1eb57b:

    # gnd "Well if you need someone to study with, you can come hang out with me pretty much any weekday night while my dad's at work."
    gnd "Eh bien, si tu as besoin de quelqu'un avec qui étudier, tu peux venir passer du temps avec moi pratiquement tous les soirs de la semaine pendant que mon père est au travail."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:86
translate french jamiephone1_b0435202:

    # pc "That sounds fun."
    pc "Ça a l'air sympa."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:87
translate french jamiephone1_d41eb353:

    # gnd "I don't know about fun. It's studying. But I'd be glad to help you."
    gnd "Je ne sais pas si c'est amusant. C'est du travail. Mais je serais ravie de t'aider."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:88
translate french jamiephone1_57376a44:

    # pc "Thanks, Jamie, I'll probably take you up on that."
    pc "Merci, Jamie, je vais probablement te prendre au mot."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:89
translate french jamiephone1_6b6bc48a:

    # gnd "I hope so."
    gnd "J'espère bien."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:91
translate french jamiephone1_1b403d26:

    # gnd "Alright, [pcname], thanks for listening. It's getting pretty late, I better go to bed."
    gnd "D'accord, [pcname], merci de m'avoir écoutée. Il se fait tard, je ferais mieux d'aller me coucher."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:92
translate french jamiephone1_fb7cffd0:

    # pc "Okay, good night."
    pc "D'accord, bonne nuit."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:93
translate french jamiephone1_e206e304:

    # gnd "Night, [pcname]."
    gnd "Bonne nuit, [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:95
translate french jamiephone1_6865bc2c:

    # "She hangs up and I put the phone on my nightstand. She's right, it is getting pretty late. Better get ready for bed."
    "Elle raccroche et je pose le téléphone sur ma table de chevet. Elle a raison, il se fait vraiment tard. Je ferais mieux de me préparer à aller me coucher."

